Note: Debug and Performance Monitoring Functions
Process called "create_code_generation_debug_tracer" returns CodeGenerationDebugTracer:
    Return CodeGenerationDebugTracer with:
        trace_level as "info"
        trace_output as list containing
        generation_events as list containing
